for a cause that is right.

08:42.230 --> 08:45.142
She has proved herself
to be a worthy daughter.

08:48.570 --> 08:50.276
It will not be forgotten.

08:51.322 --> 08:53.358
I will double the patrols on the border.

08:53.533 --> 08:56.070
We will be ready
for when Arthur returns.

08:59.831 --> 09:01.867
