09:38.578 --> 09:39.988
Get up.

09:47.504 --> 09:50.496
Not so much
of the great warrior now...

09:50.673 --> 09:52.789
Are you? Ha, ha, hal

09:52.967 --> 09:54.002
Merlin: Here

09:55.095 --> 09:56.676
I'll help him.

10:04.646 --> 10:06.136
