10:20.745 --> 10:23.452
- Milady.
- Sefa.

10:23.790 --> 10:25.405
You asked to see me.

10:26.000 --> 10:27.786
I'm sorry for what I did.

10:29.295 --> 10:31.126
It was wrong, I know.

10:31.297 --> 10:32.582
It was without thinking.

10:33.091 --> 10:35.924
I didn't mean to hurt anyone.
I wouldn't. I...

10:36.928 --> 10:39.419
All I wanted was to help my father.

10:40.682 --> 10:42.013
