10:42.183 --> 10:43.764
Gwen:
You understand the law, sefa.

10:44.227 --> 10:46.058
I cannot change it. Please

10:46.521 --> 10:48.261
I know you have a good heart.

10:48.606 --> 10:50.813
A reprieve... I'm begging you.

10:51.526 --> 10:53.733
- Men have died.
- I know.

10:55.822 --> 10:57.858
I'm sorry. I'm s...

10:58.116 --> 10:59.401
I'm so sorry.

11:05.707 --> 11:07.698
It was the only thing
he wanted from me.

11:08.459 --> 11:10.165
I told him I couldn't, but...

11:10.420 --> 11:11.956
I don't know. He...

11:13.381 --> 11:15.417
I wanted to make him happy...

11:16.176 --> 11:17.461
To please him.

11:17.635 --> 11:19.717
- He used you.
- I know.

11:20.930 --> 11:22.761
Milady, I don't want to die.

11:25.977 --> 11:27.387
There's nothing I can do, sefa.

11:27.729 --> 11:29.845
- The sentence stands.
- Milady.

11:42.785 --> 11:44.525
