11:46.331 --> 11:48.617
Perhaps you should reconsider.

11:48.791 --> 11:50.076
That sentence is a harsh one.

11:50.710 --> 11:53.543
- The law is clear.
- Sefa was naive and foolish

11:53.713 --> 11:55.328
but she doesn't deserve to die.

11:56.633 --> 12:00.501
And she won't, Gaius.
I have no intention of executing her.

12:01.596 --> 12:02.836
My aim is to catch her father.

12:03.014 --> 12:05.300
He is the threat to Camelot,
not the girl.

12:05.767 --> 12:08.133
I'm hoping her plight
will lure him here.

12:08.353 --> 12:09.718
Why did you not tell me this?

12:09.896 --> 12:11.727
Her predicament must remain genuine.

12:11.940 --> 12:15.228
If ruadan has one spy in Camelot,
he may have others.

12:15.401 --> 12:17.892
