What happens if ruadan doesn't appear?

12:27.705 --> 12:31.539
Sefa is his daughter.
I have to believe that he will

12:49.560 --> 12:51.050
Who did this?

12:52.480 --> 12:53.560
Who?!

12:55.358 --> 12:56.689
We need to rest

13:00.697 --> 13:02.904
right. You can rest...

13:03.199 --> 13:04.439
Forever.

13:18.840 --> 13:20.501
Arthur: Run! Run!

13:34.772 --> 13:37.184
- You've got to be joking.
- Do you have a better solution?

13:51.914 --> 13:53.870
We haven't got all day, Merlin.

14:17.732 --> 14:20.394
- I'll make sure they can't get across.
- Right!

15:00.525 --> 15:02.061
Why did you spare his life?

15:02.235 --> 15:04.715
- He couldn't come after us.
- He was leading us to our deaths!

15:04.779 --> 15:06.819
