15:14.372 --> 15:18.240
I love your optimism.
Come on, we need to keep moving.

15:33.474 --> 15:35.385
You have nothing to fear.

15:37.603 --> 15:39.935
Your wounds are not yet healed.

15:40.356 --> 15:42.017
You.

15:42.942 --> 15:44.182
You saved me.

15:45.111 --> 15:50.606
- Thank you.
- I know that you are worthy of my help.

15:51.451 --> 15:53.783
I don't understand.
You think kindness.

15:53.995 --> 15:57.158
Is the preserve of humans?

15:59.834 --> 16:02.120
I've never seen a creature
like you before.

16:02.545 --> 16:03.705
No

16:04.088 --> 16:05.419
Who are you?

16:05.631 --> 16:12.423
I have been called many things
by the children of men.

16:13.431 --> 16:16.673
I am the last of my kind.

16:17.643 --> 16:21.761
Once we were revered by all.

16:22.565 --> 16:26.729
But those days are long gone.

16:27.236 --> 16:30.023
For hundreds of years, we were shunned...

16:30.198 --> 16:34.532
And hunted till I found myself...

16:34.785 --> 16:36.901
Alone.

16:37.330 --> 16:41.664
And now, even this last refuge...

16:42.210 --> 16:45.623
1s safe no more.

16:54.764 --> 16:58.473
You are weak, fair knight.

16:59.268 --> 17:05.012
