26:02.102 --> 26:03.433
Genius, Merlin.

26:08.776 --> 26:10.186
(Senius?

26:11.070 --> 26:12.981
You have a bit of, um...

26:13.405 --> 26:15.145
Carrot in your hair.

26:16.158 --> 26:17.773
At least I hope it's carrot.

26:37.930 --> 26:40.546
Arthur: Ready? Merlin: For what?

26:41.433 --> 26:43.424
Our carriage awaits.

26:47.815 --> 26:49.305
Come on!

27:13.006 --> 27:14.871
Merlin:
The place is crawling with saxons.

27:15.050 --> 27:17.507
Arthur:
We'd better make sure we blend in.

27:17.678 --> 27:18.758
Arthur.

27:18.929 --> 27:22.217
Man:
Let the lady morgana see for herself.

27:25.853 --> 27:28.640
I'll get twice that
at the market at asgorath.

27:38.365 --> 27:39.650
It

