29:04.660 --> 29:05.695
Come here.

29:22.636 --> 29:23.921
I feared you were dead.

29:27.391 --> 29:29.256
It's dangerous
for those of us with magic.

29:29.977 --> 29:31.592
It's not been easy.

29:32.604 --> 29:34.060
For any of us.

29:35.232 --> 29:37.723
Sorcery frightens people.

29:40.070 --> 29:42.026
Even some of those
who claim to support it.

29:42.656 --> 29:43.816
You see 3 lot

29:44.658 --> 29:46.114
I've learned too.

29:48.203 --> 29:49.864
I have had to.

29:51.540 --> 29:55.499
If I was not to be burned at the stake
or exploited for another man's gain.

29:55.711 --> 29:57.576
Attitudes will change soon.

29:58.422 --> 30:00.663
The old religion
will reign once more.

30:00.841 --> 30:04.129
There'll be nothing to fear once Arthur
and his kind are cleansed from the earth.

