33:30.842 --> 33:32.582
Merlin: What was that?
Arthur: What?

33:36.723 --> 33:38.259
Feel the wind.

33:40.894 --> 33:42.805
Gwaine: That wasn't the wind.

34:06.878 --> 34:10.666
