Merlin!

34:29.734 --> 34:31.224
I'm going after him.

35:05.604 --> 35:07.219
Aithusa.

35:26.124 --> 35:27.705
What happened?

35:32.797 --> 35:34.503
Who did this to you?

35:36.426 --> 35:38.166
I won't harm you.

