37:00.176 --> 37:01.916
But we are brother and sister.

37:02.387 --> 37:05.220
Funny how you choose to remember that
with my dagger at your back.

37:07.183 --> 37:09.344
What happened to you, morgana?

37:09.728 --> 37:12.686
As a child, you were so kind,
so compassionate.

37:14.023 --> 37:15.183
