than you could ever imagine.

37:24.409 --> 37:27.947
And yet with all that,
you choose to do nothing but hate.

37:28.955 --> 37:30.411
Uther taught me well.

37:32.250 --> 37:34.741
- Goodbye, Arthur pendragon.
Merlin: Arthur!

37:37.589 --> 37:38.589
Merlin: Whoa!

37:44.512 --> 37:45.547
Morgana.

37:52.353 --> 37:53.388
Please.

37:55.148 --> 37:57.139
Don't speak, dear brother.

37:58.902 --> 38:00.392
It's too late.

38:19.130 --> 38:20.540
Mordred?

38:56.876 --> 38:58.241
Arthur.

39:37.792 --> 39:39.453
Emrys.

39:41.087 --> 39:42.452
Be still.

39:43.131 --> 39:46.123
Much blood has been shed this day...

39:47.093 --> 39:49.254
And all for something...

39:50.096 --> 39:53.554
Few wise men would ever want.

39:53.933 --> 39:55.673
You mean the diamair?

39:58.104 --> 40:00.095
Morgana never found it.

40:01.149 --> 40:03.481
And she never will

40:05.987 --> 40:07.318
because it is you.

40:08.781 --> 40:11.238
You are the key to all knowledge.

40:13.536 --> 40:17.745
There are times when I feel the weight
of my destiny crushing me...

40:18.666 --> 40:20.327
But that's nothing to what you carry.

40:20.543 --> 40:22.955
It is both a blessing...

40:23.755 --> 40:25.336
And

40:26.633 --> 40:28.498
a curse.

40:30.053 --> 40:33.762
Is there anything you wish to ask me?

40:35.058 --> 40:36.389
No

40:39.187 --> 40:41.394
I don't think it would be good.

40:43.775 --> 40:46.767
You are wise, emrys.

40:46.945 --> 40:49.607
Your wisdom will live long...

40:49.822 --> 40:51.778
In the minds of men.

40:55.036 --> 40:56.401
Wait

40:58.289 --> 41:00.120
there is one question.

41:04.337 --> 41:07.249
If mordred is not Arthur's bane,
then who is?

41:26.859 --> 41:29.692
Arise, sir mordred...

41:30.488 --> 41:32.444
Knight of Camelot.

41:48.715 --> 41:50.296
Here

41:51.342 --> 41:53.424
let me help you with that.

41:57.181 --> 41:58.717
Thank you.

42:00.643 --> 42:06.058
You know, if Arthur knew you had magic,
things would be very different.

42:13.531 --> 42:15.442
Tell me something.

42:16.325 --> 42:17.815
Of course.

42:17.994 --> 42:20.610
You saved Arthur's life

42:21.539 --> 42:23.245
why?

42:24.876 --> 42:26.787
Because Arthur is right.

42:27.587 --> 42:30.044
The love that binds us
is more important...

42:30.256 --> 42:32.372
Than the power we wield.

42:35.386 --> 42:36.922
Morgana had forgotten that.

42:54.739 --> 42:56.730
It's been a big day. You must be tired.

42:57.867 --> 42:59.323
Too tired for pudding?

42:59.994 --> 43:01.700
Is there pudding?

43:03.664 --> 43:05.325
Is that my favorite?

43:11.255 --> 43:13.462
So are you going to tell me
what's troubling you?

43:14.759 --> 43:16.590
Mordred.

43:19.222 --> 43:20.758
People change.

43:22.975 --> 43:26.183
Perhaps you should give him
the benefit of the doubt.

43:29.398 --> 43:31.480
Remember what the dragon said?

43:32.485 --> 43:34.476
Arthur would meet his end
at the hands of a druid.

43:34.654 --> 43:37.020
You still believe that's him?

43:38.074 --> 43:40.065
I feel that the die is cast.

43:41.119 --> 43:43.075
And that for good or ill...

43:43.913 --> 43:46.620
Albion's great trial has begun.

44:18.489 --> 44:20.025
It has the power...

44:20.283 --> 44:22.649
To summon the spirits
of the dead

44:23.452 --> 44:24.487
ohl

44:32.837 --> 44:34.373
I know it's you, father.
